OL,5, Tributes are being paid to the South   
OL,6, African playwright Mbongeni Ngema after
OL,7, he died in a car crash aged 68.        
OL,9,FHe rose to international prominence in 
OL,10,Fthe 1980s with plays that depicted the 
OL,11,Flives of black people under the racist 
OL,12,Fsystem of apartheid.                   
OL,14,FHis works "reflected the spirit of     
OL,15,Fresistance" during white minority rule,
OL,16,Fhis family said.                       
OL,18,FNgema was best-known for his musical   
OL,19,FSarafina!, which was later adapted into
OL,20,Fa film starring Whoopi Goldberg.       
